frames.caption: A surreal image depicts a close-up of a human eye with a clock face replacing the iris and pupil. The clock hands are prominently visible, suggesting the passage of time. The monochromatic tones add to the dreamlike and introspective quality of the scene.
frames.description: The scene is a surreal and artistic representation, blending human anatomy with the concept of time. The focus is on the eye, which is transformed into a clock, symbolizing the intertwining of human perception and the relentless passage of time.
